reviewText: Never actually bought the DVD from here though I was thinking of getting it at some point from a reliable source. The other reviews clearly got the wrong show. It's not a movie, it's a drama about 3 siblings who's parents were murdered. It shows this at the beginning and then it does a 14 year time skip.

Some lights in the dark. Smoke from nowhere in particular, the camera shaking to imply that the world is shaking. Children are born. Suddenly it is years later. Some people have mental powers. Dead people rising. A village is punish for its sins. BAD story, BAD directing, BAD acting. BAD movie. I repeat NO METEOR. Service however was good. DVD got here fast. DVD in good condition.
